ate than using CEP. The implementation of the DET scheme is\nexperimentally feasible as tested on IBM's quantum computation platform.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Oct 2021 03:29:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 18 Apr 2022 15:43:50 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 15 Mar 2023 05:05:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-06-05"}
