echanism. In the\nintermediate regime, the evolution is profile-dependent and no unique DVDR\nexists.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Oct 2021 09:57:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 4 Jan 2022 11:55:29 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 3 Feb 2022 12:51:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-24"}
