ues\", \"establishing a dedicated team/person for values concerns\") to address\nBangladeshi female farmers' values in agriculture apps.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Oct 2021 10:51:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-12"}
