cal blockchain technology due to several disadvantages in practical\nimplementation. Decryption latency, massive consumption of computational\nresources, and increased key size are few challenges that can hinder blockchain\nperformance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Oct 2021 14:41:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-12"}
